  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this protocol is to determine whether Tacrolimus and Prednisolone are
      effective and safe in the treatment of the cyclophosphamide-resistant, refractory diffuse
      proliferative lupus nephritis
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
